{"tid":1976440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共：CDC緊隨中國發病毒警告 美撤外交人員 美禁中國人入境 三證中方助美抗疫","createTime":"2020-04-17T08:52:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T09:15:08.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ab150929066ab20af8e204706469faa7bdca2115","tid":1976440,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:52:41.000Z","msg":"外交部對美方指稱遭誤導疫情提出3點質疑<br />\n17.04.2020 16:44<br />\n<br />\n美國新型冠狀病毒疫情依然嚴峻，累計病例超過67萬宗，3.3萬人不治，確診及死亡數字是全球最多，總統特朗普及華府高層相繼批評中方隱瞞疫情，誤導美國，在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅作出反駁，指抹黑污名化掩蓋不了事實，栽贓趕不走病毒，奉勸美方停止政治操弄，把精力更多放在如何盡快戰勝病毒和提振經濟。<br />\n<br />\n趙立堅就美方聲稱在疫情初期受到誤導的講法提出3點質疑，包括美國疾控中心為何在1月15日就發布病毒警告、美方為何在1月25日關閉駐武漢總領館並撤出人員，及為何在2月2日禁止到過中國的人士入境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281506&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281506%26csid%3D261_341&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=346c8d75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281506&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"3b48b04aa6507c44e08f69f16bbc1097c7f194f5","tid":1976440,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:53:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdd0ce2221e364d101d8b9cc11eb106a3ca03f3","tid":1976440,"uid":132438,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HL86Get.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHL86Get.jpg&h=901bf3b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSJymet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSJymet.jpg&h=1d49b486&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kj5dmeu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkj5dmeu.jpg&h=182dcc15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d14f403d4269232b926f3303d8da2e31a374911","tid":1976440,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"15號你都已經爆撚到9彩"},{"pid":"571d0383d42e2a2890183134d5ab8070dabb2ebd","tid":1976440,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:55:15.000Z","msg":"潑婦罵街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acd0c14bd3dc997bae236da95e3bf218a8b5dda3","tid":1976440,"uid":47042,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"咪就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">遲撚左</span></span>囉<br />\n<br />\n12月既連登已經講緊人傳人<br />\n唔知邊個抗疫強國一月仲話無人傳人？"},{"pid":"53128022e65e43a6d9e1d0e1ae4e52908f3e8e96","tid":1976440,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda5e09780758fcba8e3d2f8f67a1be2f5112b29","tid":1976440,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:05:10.000Z","msg":"美國疾控中心為何在1月15日就發布病毒警告、美方為何在1月25日關閉駐武漢總領館並撤出人員，及為何在2月2日禁止到過中國的人士入境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咦  幫侵侵助選喎  岩呀  係歐洲班白皮豬傳入美國架  咁又點？<br />\n乜原來連支共都知  美國係全球第一個國家禁中國的人士入境？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁d左膠係咁鬧侵侵慢  到底佢慢左d乜？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 第一個都慢 ？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd60106f99c6a66d5ad6aa5145511d36264f6b6","tid":1976440,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"趙立堅呢隻支那賤畜出返嚟<br />\n就代表習近平想盡地一鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245b49fc59b33e2bead28e28c469020a34355e4e","tid":1976440,"uid":81052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:07:45.000Z","msg":"譚德塞指世衛不主張從武漢撤僑<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378428\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378428&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=4471884b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378428&h=eea8e362\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=378428</a>"},{"pid":"bef4316d600998e79d4f171afc18f185027d463b","tid":1976440,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"中共：你經濟唔好累到我呀，屌你<br />\n<br />\n外交部批評美暗示病毒來自武漢實驗室是要推卸責任<br />\n17.04.2020 17:04<br />\n<br />\n美國新型冠狀病毒疫情依然嚴峻，累計病例超過67萬宗，3.3萬人不治，確診及死亡數字是全球最多，總統特朗普及華府高層相繼批評中方隱瞞疫情，誤導美國，在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅作出反駁，就美方的講法提出3點質疑，包括美國疾控中心為何在1月15日就發布病毒警告、美方為何在1月25日關閉駐武漢總領館並撤出人員，及為何在2月2日禁止到過中國的人士入境。他指抹黑污名化掩蓋不了事實，栽贓趕不走病毒，奉勸美方停止政治操弄，<span style=\"color: gold;\">把精力更多放在如何盡快戰勝病毒和提振經濟。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於美國國務卿蓬佩奧暗示，新型冠狀病毒可能來自武漢實驗室，趙立堅指，美方的目的是要轉移視線，推卸責任，重申病毒溯源是嚴肅的科學問題，需要聽取科學和尊重科學專業的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281515&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281515%26csid%3D261_341&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=6582c178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281515&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c26e6a1b4ba7f93440ee1a59dc9ba3dae5081edf","tid":1976440,"uid":44309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:15:08.000Z","msg":"冇畀你呃到，同你有冇呃人，係兩回事嚟。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"bef4316d600998e79d4f171afc18f185027d463b","tid":1976440,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"中共：你經濟唔好累到我呀，屌你<br />\n<br />\n外交部批評美暗示病毒來自武漢實驗室是要推卸責任<br />\n17.04.2020 17:04<br />\n<br />\n美國新型冠狀病毒疫情依然嚴峻，累計病例超過67萬宗，3.3萬人不治，確診及死亡數字是全球最多，總統特朗普及華府高層相繼批評中方隱瞞疫情，誤導美國，在北京，外交部發言人趙立堅作出反駁，就美方的講法提出3點質疑，包括美國疾控中心為何在1月15日就發布病毒警告、美方為何在1月25日關閉駐武漢總領館並撤出人員，及為何在2月2日禁止到過中國的人士入境。他指抹黑污名化掩蓋不了事實，栽贓趕不走病毒，奉勸美方停止政治操弄，<span style=\"color: gold;\">把精力更多放在如何盡快戰勝病毒和提振經濟。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於美國國務卿蓬佩奧暗示，新型冠狀病毒可能來自武漢實驗室，趙立堅指，美方的目的是要轉移視線，推卸責任，重申病毒溯源是嚴肅的科學問題，需要聽取科學和尊重科學專業的意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281515&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1281515%26csid%3D261_341&d=5Vq0xNKZ3qFPdYugipJU98dEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=6582c178\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1281515&amp;csid=261_341</a>"}}